South Africa's Estate Agency Affairs Board Is Probing Four Estate Agencies

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-03-02T08:37:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-02/south-africa-s-estate-agency-affairs-board-probing-four-estate-agencies.html
  South Africa ’s Minister of Trade and
Industry Rob Davies said the country’s regulator is
investigating four estate agencies, according to a statement
e-mailed to Bloomberg News today.  Davies said, in response to a question in parliament, that
the agencies were being probed by the Estate Agency Affairs
Board on the possibility of an improper use of trust funds.  To contact the reporter on this story:
